  ('social-worker-moex-07830', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-099-a62ebd66', 'sub-social-worker-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '做研究的過程需要一系列的步驟，下列那一順序的步驟是正確？', '["聚焦研究問題→選擇研究主題→研究設計→蒐集資料→分析資料→解釋資料→發表", "選擇研究主題→聚焦研究問題→蒐集資料→研究設計→分析資料→解釋資料→發表", "聚焦研究問題→選擇研究主題→蒐集資料→研究設計→分析資料→解釋資料→發表", "選擇研究主題→聚焦研究問題→研究設計→蒐集資料→分析資料→解釋資料→發表"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:39+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "01a38a7597b2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "7b44c41cbb23", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "099010", "c": "902", "s": "700", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作研究方法", "year": "099", "exam_name": "099年第一次醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、語言治療師、醫師分試、社會工作師", "original_question_number": 18, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-07831', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-099-a62ebd66', 'sub-social-worker-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '研究者確定研究題目後，進一步的工作就是設定研究假設，因此建構假設時應該遵守的標準有：①概念', '["實證基礎", "明確化", "資料收集要有可行性  ⑤與理論無關，下列那一組答案正確？", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:39+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "01a38a7597b2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "7b44c41cbb23", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "099010", "c": "902", "s": "700", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作研究方法", "year": "099", "exam_name": "099年第一次醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、語言治療師、醫師分試、社會工作師", "original_question_number": 19, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-07832', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-099-a62ebd66', 'sub-social-worker-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '以下何者最正確？①受的教育越多，結婚越晚  ②現在年紀越大的受訪者，初婚年齡越早  ③男性平均', '["每天多看一小時電視，初婚年齡平均晚0.058年", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:39+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "01a38a7597b2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "7b44c41cbb23", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "099010", "c": "902", "s": "700", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作研究方法", "year": "099", "exam_name": "099年第一次醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、語言治療師、醫師分試、社會工作師", "original_question_number": 20, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-07833', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-099-a62ebd66', 'sub-social-worker-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '表中R2=0.27代表：', '["4個自變項可以解釋依變項總變異量的27%", "4個自變項中有27%可以解釋依變項的變異量", "4個自變項與依變項的總相關係數等於0.27", "27%的受訪者初婚婚齡受此4個自變項的影響"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:39+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "01a38a7597b2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "7b44c41cbb23", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "099010", "c": "902", "s": "700", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作研究方法", "year": "099", "exam_name": "099年第一次醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、語言治療師、醫師分試、社會工作師", "original_question_number": 21, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-07834', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-099-a62ebd66', 'sub-social-worker-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '4個自變項中對婚齡影響力最大的是：', '["性別", "年齡", "受教育年數", "每天看電視時數"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:39+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "01a38a7597b2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "7b44c41cbb23", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "099010", "c": "902", "s": "700", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作研究方法", "year": "099", "exam_name": "099年第一次醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、語言治療師、醫師分試、社會工作師", "original_question_number": 22, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-07835', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-099-a62ebd66', 'sub-social-worker-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '受到2008年金融海嘯的影響，臺灣地區失業率創歷史新高，若研究者想要瞭解在這次的金融海嘯中，臺 灣的那些企業受到衝擊最大，其分析單位應該是：', '["個人", "團體", "組織", "社會人為事實"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:39+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "01a38a7597b2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "7b44c41cbb23", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "099010", "c": "902", "s": "700", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作研究方法", "year": "099", "exam_name": "099年第一次醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、語言治療師、醫師分試、社會工作師", "original_question_number": 23, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-07836', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-099-a62ebd66', 'sub-social-worker-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列那一個抽樣方法不是「非隨機抽樣法」？', '["便利抽樣（convenience sampling）", "系統抽樣（systematic sampling）", "配額抽樣（quota sampling）", "滾雪球抽樣（snowball sampling）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:39+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "01a38a7597b2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "7b44c41cbb23", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "099010", "c": "902", "s": "700", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作研究方法", "year": "099", "exam_name": "099年第一次醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、語言治療師、醫師分試、社會工作師", "original_question_number": 24, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-07837', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-099-a62ebd66', 'sub-social-worker-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '信度指的是從同一個測量取得一致的結果；效度指的是能夠正確反應被測量概念的結果。而有關信度、 效度的敘述，何者是正確？', '["效標關聯效度（criterion-related validity）是根據變項之間的邏輯關係而形成的效度", "建構效度（construct validity）是根據一些外在的效標所決定的效度", "重測信度（test-retest reliability）是指在兩種不同情況下，針對同一個人分別測試，兩個相關值必須在", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:39+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "01a38a7597b2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "7b44c41cbb23", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "099010", "c": "902", "s": "700", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作研究方法", "year": "099", "exam_name": "099年第一次醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、語言治療師、醫師分試、社會工作師", "original_question_number": 25, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-07838', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-099-a62ebd66', 'sub-social-worker-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '70或0.80以上', '["折半信度（split-half reliability）建構第二份量表，與第一份量表預定測量的是一樣，受訪者也一樣，由 此比較其相關性", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:39+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "01a38a7597b2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "7b44c41cbb23", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "099010", "c": "902", "s": "700", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作研究方法", "year": "099", "exam_name": "099年第一次醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、語言治療師、醫師分試、社會工作師", "original_question_number": 0, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-07839', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-099-a62ebd66', 'sub-social-worker-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '擬定研究設計時必須注意內在效度和外在效度的問題，然而會影響外在效度的因素是：', '["歷史", "成熟", "統計迴歸", "多次測量"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:39+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "01a38a7597b2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "7b44c41cbb23", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "099010", "c": "902", "s": "700", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作研究方法", "year": "099", "exam_name": "099年第一次醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、語言治療師、醫師分試、社會工作師", "original_question_number": 26, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL)
